   <concept id="FAR_47_104_4" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">47.104-4</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2724e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2751e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            In order to ensure the application of <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title49-section10721&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">49 U.S.C. 10721</xref> and <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title49-section13712&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">13712</xref> rates, where authorized (see <xref href="47.104.dita#FAR_47_104"
                        base="i1071359"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">47.104</xref>(b)), insert the clause at <xref href="52.247-1.dita#FAR_52_247_1"
                        base="i1045527"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-1</xref>, Commercial Bill of Lading Notations, in solicitations and contracts when the contracts will be-</p>
               <ol id="d2724e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2751e28">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Cost-reimbursement contracts, including those that may involve the movement of household goods (see <xref href="47.104-3.dita#FAR_47_104_3"
                              base="i1071395"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-3</xref>(b)); or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2751e36">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Fixed-price f.o.b. origin contracts (other than contracts at or below the simplified acquisition threshold) (see <xref href="47.104-2.dita#FAR_47_104_2"
                              base="i1071384"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-2</xref>(b) and <xref href="47.104-3.dita#FAR_47_104_3"
                              base="i1071395"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-3</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2751e47">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The contracting officer may insert the clause at <xref href="52.247-1.dita#FAR_52_247_1"
                        base="i1045527"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-1</xref>, Commercial Bill of Lading Notations, in solicitations and contracts made at or below the simplified acquisition threshold when it is contemplated that the delivery terms will be f.o.b. origin.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
